FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__TypedProperty_3) [p].[Id], [p].[AddDate], [p].[BathroomCount], [p].[CityId], [p].[CurrencyId], [p].[Description], [p].[DescriptionDe], [p].[DescriptionRu], [p].[DescriptionTranslateKey], [p].[DistrictId], [p].[Floor], [p].[GrossArea], [p].[IsActive], [p].[IsFavourite], [p].[IsSold], [p].[NetArea], [p].[Price], [p].[PriceDinar], [p].[PriceEur], [p].[ProjectDate], [p].[ProjectNumber], [p].[ProjectStatus], [p].[ProjectTye], [p].[SaloonCount], [p].[SeeClose], [p].[StreetId], [p].[Title], [p].[TitleDe], [p].[TitleRu], [p].[TitleTranslateKey], [p].[TownId], [p].[Year], [p].[ZipCode]
    FROM [Project].[Project] AS [p]
    WHERE ([p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)) AND (([p].[IsActive] = @__TypedProperty_1) AND ([p].[ProjectTye] = CAST(1 AS tinyint)))
    ORDER BY [p].[AddDate] DESC

INNER JOIN [Address].[District] AS [d] ON [t].[DistrictId] = [d].[Id]

) AS [t1] ON ([t].[Id] = [t1].[ProjectId]) AND ([t].[Id] = [t1].[ProjectId])
LEFT JOIN [Feature] AS [f] ON [t].[Id] = [f].[ProjectId]
ORDER BY [t].[AddDate] DESC, [t].[Id], [c].[Id], [d].[Id], [s].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t1].[Id]
